title: The JRE review of 1271 with Billy Corben
description:
Billy Corben made Cocaine Cowboys 1 & 2 and now has a new baseball documentary out that discusses the doping scandals. He’s a very smart dude and a great conversationalist. This is a really fun podcast to review. Check out Joe’s conversation now.
